OL,4,Cwithout consent appealed
OL,6,FIn their ruling, the MPT Service
OL,7,Fstated that the gynaecologist had
OL,8,F"shown good insight into his failures
OL,9,F(...) and put in place procedures and
OL,10,Factions to address his failings to
OL,11,Fensure they do not happen again".
OL,13,FFollowing the result, an online
OL,14,Fpetition garnered more than 22,000
OL,15,Fsignatures, calling for Dr Shokouh-
OL,16,FAmiri's medical license to be revoked.
